The proposal includes extending this reservation to educational institutions, drawing parallels with Tamil Nadu and Jharkhand's higher reservation percentages. The survey, initiated in 2015 and completed in February 2024, places the OBC population at over 4.16 crore.
title: Karnataka caste census recommends raising Backward Class reservations to 51%

description: Lok Sabha Speaker Om Birla honored his promise to the family of Pulwama martyr Hemraj by performing the Mayra ceremony at his daughter's wedding in Kota. Fulfilling the role of a maternal uncle, Birla supported Hemraj's widow, Madhubala, and presented traditional wedding gifts.
title: LS Speaker Om Birla fulfils brotherly promise at Pulwama martyr daughter’s wedding

description: A Russian missile struck a warehouse belonging to Kusum Healthcare, an Indian pharmaceutical company, in Ukraine, prompting condemnation from the Ukrainian embassy, which alleged a deliberate targeting of Indian businesses. title: Ukraine says Russian strike hit Indian pharma firm warehouse: What we know

description: A twin-engine Mitsubishi MU-2B aircraft crashed in a muddy field near Copake, upstate New York, on Saturday, with two people on board.
